This paper deals with attribute learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper focuses on learning user-specific predictors across multiple attributes, which involves feature selection and personalized opinions. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper also involves multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) aspects, as it deals with semantic annotations and feature selection.
